Welcome to the EVIDEO


1. Installation of Matterhorn on the Server
	a. Download the Installation folder onto the System.
	b. Follow the instructions provided in the README file.
				OR
	a. Follow the steps at "http://www.opencast.org/matterhorn/"

2. After Successful Installation of Matterhorn, perform the following steps.
	
	a. Download the "evideo-modules".
	b. Copy "matterhorn-runtime-info-ui" to "/opt/matterhorn/1.x/modules/".
	c. Copy "matterhorn-engage-ui" to "/opt/matterhorn/1.x/modules/".
	d. Clean and build the above modules using "mvn clean install -DdeployTo=/opt/matterhorn/felix/matterhorn"

3. Download the "playlist-module" and copy the folder "play" to "/var/www/html/" i.e. HTTPD Server
4. Download the "php-files" and copy all the files to "/var/www/html/" i.e. HTTPD Server

5. Then Run the Project as "http://localhost:80" 
